These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, designer, manager
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, peas, lime
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, poppy
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, turquise, orange
1. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the designer is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
6. the person eating lime is the person who likes orange##1
7. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | dancer        | designer     | manager    |
| Food   | lime      | watermelon     | peas |
| Flower         | marigold | poppy | tulip   |
| Color     | orange        | turquise      | blood-red        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
City: berlin, paris, liverpool
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown, mauve
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
House: futuristic, palace, farmhouse
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
2. the person who likes mauve is between the owner of the frog and the person traveling to berlin##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| City    | paris    | liverpool | berlin |
| Color       | brown   | mauve  | fuchsia  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse    | palace        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
City: london, boston, rome
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, disaster
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, azalea
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person watching disaster movies##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| City         | rome | london | boston |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster     | crime    | adventure |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Flower           | azalea         | marigold      | daffodil    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, tulip
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, yellow, orange
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, taxi, helicopter
1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes orange is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who likes red##2
7. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Flower      | bellflower | balloon-flower       | tulip   |
| Color          | red   | orange   | yellow     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Transport   | taxi | bike | helicopter |

