.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, soccer, skateboarding
3 different games are played: whist, domino, snooker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy, orchid
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, train
1. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is soccer##2
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person playing domino and the person playing snooker##2
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
8. the person playing domino is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport      | soccer   | skateboarding    | surfing   |
| Game          | snooker | whist  | domino |
| Flower   | poppy   | aconite | orchid  |
| Transport     | roller | scooter   | train  |

