.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, domino
City: marseilles, london, venice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, marigold
1. the person eating asparagus is the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person traveling to london##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who growsmarigold and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Game           | bridge      | poker  | domino |
| City   | london  | marseilles   | venice  |
| Flower           | zinnia      | orchid | marigold        |

