.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, mango, peach
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, dahlia
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bolivar, aristoff
1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsazalea is the person eating mango##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
8. the owner of the cat is the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Food   | grapes         | peach      | mango   |
| Flower        | dahlia | amaryllis          | azalea |
| Pet        | cat         | lizard        | pony       |
| Cigar      | bolivar       | aristoff | havana       |

