.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, horror, scientific
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, teacher
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, chinese, indian
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, aquamarine, coral
1. the teacher is the person who likes brown##1
2. the indian is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes coral##1
6. the teacher is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Movie-Genre       | scientific | animation    | horror |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| Nationality         | chinese  | indian     | turkish        |
| Color   | coral       | aquamarine   | brown         |

