.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, milk
City: nizza, prague, san-francisco
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, old-henry
House: palace, ranch-style, cottage
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to prague##1
6. the palace house is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk       | coffee | almond-milk |
| City          | prague  | nizza | san-francisco   |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | old-henry   | oliveros        |
| House     | cottage | ranch-style    | palace        |

