.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, february, august
House: colonial, cottage, victorian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, vegafina, bluemaster
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the vegafina-smoker is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the cottage house##1
5. the fan of classical is the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is between the montecristo-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
7. the fan of d&b is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Birthday      | august     | february | september  |
| House          | victorian   | cottage     | colonial  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bluemaster     | vegafina   |

