.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, fanta
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, mauve, blue
3 different games are played: domino, billiard, snooker
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person who likes mauve is between the person drinking fanta and the person who likes light-blue##2
2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage       | fanta   | mirinda | tea  |
| Color         | blue      | mauve      | light-blue   |
| Game       | billiard      | snooker       | domino |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike       | tram     |

