.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, collecting, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, manager
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daffodil, aconite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, sailing, cricket
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is between the engineer and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby          | singing | chess | collecting |
| Job           | engineer   | manager   | librarian |
| Flower   | aconite     | daffodil     | lily  |
| Sport   | sailing     | cricket  | snowboarding   |

