.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, february
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, librarian
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, van
1. the librarian is between the dancer and the doctor##2
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the doctor##1
4. the librarian is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the skateboard##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the doctor##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday   | march | february    | april |
| Job       | doctor          | librarian     | dancer       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Transport        | taxi          | van       | skateboard        |

