4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person drinking tea is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | fantasy   | romance   |
