.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-15::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, tower
3 different games are played: snooker, bridge, domino
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, august, october
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
5. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person playing domino and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| House      | tower    | wooden   | farmhouse      |
| Game   | domino | snooker   | bridge |
| Birthday           | november      | october      | august      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | rugby      |

