House: cape-cod, art-deco, farmhouse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, sunflower
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, italian, german
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the russian##1
2. the german is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
5. the art-deco house is between the person who's hobby is reading and the farmhouse house##2
6. the person who growssunflower is the farmhouse house##1
7. the art-deco house is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading      | sudoku     | collecting |
| House           | cape-cod | art-deco | farmhouse     |
| Flower   | zinnia    | balloon-flower       | sunflower      |
| Nationality           | russian          | italian       | german     |

