.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-18::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, pear, strawberry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, salsa, trance
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, hamster
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, snowmobile
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the hamster and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person eating strawberry is the fan of trance##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the person eating kale is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the fan of trance is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Food      | kale    | pear        | strawberry |
| Music-Genre   | country | salsa | trance  |
| Pet         | pony  | hedgehog     | hamster |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile   | ship    |

