House: futuristic, cottage, craftsman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, fantasy
There 3 different types of food: lemon, mango, pineapple
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
4. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Cigar      | prince | tiparillo  | old-henry |
| House           | futuristic  | craftsman  | cottage      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | animation     |
| Food           | pineapple  | lemon | mango         |

 